name: Teztropolis II
description: A Tezos-themed futuristic city. Generated using kitbashed low-poly assets scattered on a plane mesh using geometry nodes. Holograms, neon, traffic, and atmospheric effects manually added. Rendered in Blender Eevee. Featured OBJKTs: #174217 "TREE X Æ HEN 200" by @MDixken and #396549 "V002" by @synesthesiaART. By Lucius Felimus: https://www.luciusfelimus.com/
